market_title: Will the S&P 500 be between 6800 and 6999.99 at the end of Dec 31, 2025?
rules_primary: If the end-of-day S&P 500 index value for December 31, 2025 is between 6800-6999.99, then the market resolves to Yes.
rules_secondary:
The market will expire at the sooner of the first 7:00 PM ET after the release of the data, or one week after December 31, 2025.

Pursuant to the Kalshi Rulebook, the Exchange has modified the Source Agency and Underlying for indices markets. See the rules for more information.
